rows.label: tlk44300083_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Ohh, my darling... Your heart is as
impenetrable as Theoscaldia... How
can I coax you to open your gates?

rows.label: tlk44300083_01_msg0002
rows.name:
...I'd thank you for not
interrupting. I'm using the
landscape here to woo my beloved.

rows.label: tlk44300083_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The city of Teos Aure is very secure...
It may be the embodiment of history,
uninterrupted since the time of Adel.

rows.label: tlk44300083_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Hoho... The more sturdy the
keep, the greater the satisfaction
does its downfall bring!
